 i\ re^{i\vartheta} = re^{i(\vartheta+\pi/2)} = -r\sin \vartheta + i r\cos\vartheta\simeq -r\sin\vartheta \frac{\partial}{\partial x}+ r\sin\vartheta\frac{\partial}{\partial y}. 
